---
title: Pan-Fried Duck Pilaf with Tomatoes and Carrot
description: Ready in just 30 minutes, our pan-fried duck pilaf is a sweet and succulent dish that delivers on taste. Seasoned with garlic and pasanda spice blend, the Indian spice takes duck to the next level, drawing out its naturally sweet and rich flavour. Our chefs have chosen to pan fry the meat for a deliciously crispy outer texture. Combine with basmati rice, raisins and fresh carrot and a drizzle of yoghurt for a dish that ticks all the boxes.
